{"annotations":[{"start_time":0,"end_time":3,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"How did you learn to sign?"}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Interviewer محاور","tag":"Ghofran"}],"uuid":"581fcd1e-1da7-4afa-899a-02bf3b37306f"},{"start_time":2,"end_time":5,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"I learned because my parents are Deaf."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"86713036-c8a5-41fe-a853-e072dab7fa7e"},{"start_time":5,"end_time":11,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"I developed my signing from my parents and then I enrolled in the Al-Amal school for the Deaf and kept learning their from my peers."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"ec7b3179-44d0-4cc2-8961-2413d80840e3"},{"start_time":20,"end_time":21,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"What about you?"}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Interviewer محاور","tag":"Ghofran"}],"uuid":"88c440e1-abae-459b-9289-515f31eb0534"},{"start_time":20,"end_time":26,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"When I first started school, my signing wasn't very strong yet..."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"1b0b49d8-ba74-405e-a17d-7071364c99cb"},{"start_time":27,"end_time":33,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"I was progressing with learning to sign when I found out that the Association is here in Mansheyya so I went here and developed a lot more."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"919aa9aa-d98e-43f4-9d8b-f5d7008db08a"},{"start_time":38,"end_time":45,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Hey, Tell him that the association here is like our mother."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"d27eca04-53c9-40ff-afcb-8efaec98d468"},{"start_time":45,"end_time":51,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Hey- So in school we just learn a little bit. After finishing school, we go to the association."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"521db474-2a89-4a94-accb-80b424ae7e7b"},{"start_time":52,"end_time":59,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"This place is where they learn. This place is the mother to all the Alexandrian Deaf community. Does he understand?"}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"2dc818bc-e783-45b0-b774-e6d34c0c9e96"},{"start_time":63,"end_time":69,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"The association is old-- it's been here since 1957."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"f4749130-09c0-40b6-8e8d-b081df1e562b"},{"start_time":86,"end_time":93,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Hey, so there's a Deaf school and there's a Hard of Hearing school and in the end they both come here to the Association."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"604e254a-49c4-4927-8c03-fd28e71d733e"},{"start_time":101,"end_time":105,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"At the school, the education isn't so good."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"5d998a3d-7510-46e8-b23a-eb55f1fd6198"},{"start_time":105,"end_time":108,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"The association plans Deaf Education."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"901e7319-d341-4e6e-b8f5-90726f7c489a"},{"start_time":108,"end_time":111,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Here we take care of psychological needs."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"487a4584-cf4f-4103-b6ba-07fb662bf0c3"},{"start_time":111,"end_time":118,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Our education and development is in a huge part thanks to this place!"}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"87bad4b9-b758-46e5-876b-abd7c280c023"},{"start_time":169,"end_time":174,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Can you read and write Arabic well, or not?"}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Interviewer محاور","tag":"Ghofran"}],"uuid":"7cf4ad04-e23d-4e90-adf8-e69db5358ea2"},{"start_time":173,"end_time":179,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"In school here there is no proper upbringing at all-- zero at all."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"0ab5ef8d-2007-45e2-a425-88df45daeda3"},{"start_time":179,"end_time":184,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"I was motivated to learn myself."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"d9272c00-deb2-4f97-b9d6-7fe216fd505c"},{"start_time":184,"end_time":188,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Regarding learning, my parents taught me a little bit, and I add a bit to that bit myself."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"4ece1ba0-9558-4ff1-9359-75e07d197d01"},{"start_time":188,"end_time":192,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"That's all."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"0f5dc469-bf5b-490b-8c1f-89dca0e1dc65"},{"start_time":192,"end_time":194,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Also, I'm strong in mathematics."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Abdelaziz"}],"uuid":"527b8ef7-2711-428c-b9b8-4de07690083e"},{"start_time":197,"end_time":205,"annotation":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"If I read something and don't know a word, my hearing brother tells me and then I know it. But at the Al-Amal School for the Deaf there was never education."}]}],"tags":[{"category":"Participant مشارك","tag":"Eslam"}],"uuid":"633b2775-eb1b-489f-865d-60856d1f4475"}],"event_id":"53c07a5b-15b5-4873-9643-5713b9744bac","set":"English","source_id":"0f74d97a-bcaf-418e-a035-f6ba5dc534f1"}